KSE to Buy Arsenal in Transaction Valuing Club at $1.1 Billion

-- B y   D a r a   D o y l e
-- 
2011-04-11T06:06:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-11/kse-agrees-to-buy-arsenal-in-transaction-valuing-soccer-club-1-1-billion.html
 KSE and Arsenal said they agreed
the terms of a recommended mandatory cash offer to be made by
KSE for Arsenal.  For each Arsenal Share, Arsenal shareholders
will receive 11,750 pounds in cash, valuing the club at about
731 million pounds.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dara Doyle at 
